vote.title: Authorize a public hearing to be held on August 24, 2022, to receive comments on re-adopting and continuing in effect Chapter 12, City Youth Program Standards of Care, of the Dallas City Code, to re-establish standards of care for certain city youth programs in compliance with state law; and, at the close of the public hearing, approval of an ordinance to readopt Chapter 12 of the Dallas City Code - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
